                "category": "details",
                "text": "MEGATRONBRIDGE:Megatron Bridge",
                "title": "Product Team"
            },
            {
                "category": "summary",
                "text": "NVIDIA has released a software update for NVIDIA\u00ae Megatron Bridge.&nbsp;<div>To protect your system, clone or update this software to version 0.4.1 or later from the <a href=\"https://github.com/NVIDIA-NeMo/Megatron-Bridge\">NVIDIA/Megatron-Bridge</a> GitHub repo.</div>",
                "title": "Summary"
            },
            {
                "category": "details",
                "text": "NVIDIA has released a software update for NVIDIA\u00ae Megatron Bridge.&nbsp;<div>To protect your system, clone or update this software to version 0.4.1 or later from the <a href=\"https://github.com/NVIDIA-NeMo/Megatron-Bridge\">NVIDIA/Megatron-Bridge</a> GitHub repo.</div>",
                "title": "Security Update Notes"
            },
